{
  "page": "Wise Women",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>Wise Women</b> were the retinue of women sent to <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a> by Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Regent\" title=\"Regent\">Regent</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Alyssa_Velaryon\" title=\"Alyssa Velaryon\">Alyssa Velaryon</a> to serve as attendants and companions to her daughter, Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Alysanne_Targaryen\" title=\"Alysanne Targaryen\">Alysanne Targaryen</a>. Their nickname came from the <i><a href=\"/index.php/Wise_Woman\" title=\"Wise Woman\">Wise Woman</a></i>, the trading galley that took them from <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> to Dragonstone.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Members\">Members</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wise_Women&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Members\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Ysabel\" title=\"Ysabel\">Ysabel</a>, a <a href=\"/index.php/Septa\" title=\"Septa\">septa</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">Faith of the Seven</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lyra\" title=\"Lyra\">Lyra</a>, a novice of the Faith</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Edyth\" title=\"Edyth\">Edyth</a>, a novice of the Faith</li>\n<li>Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Lucinda_Broome\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lucinda Broome\">Lucinda</a>, wife of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Prentys_Tully\" title=\"Prentys Tully\">Prentys Tully</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a>, famed for her piety</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jennis_Templeton\" title=\"Jennis Templeton\">Jennis Templeton</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Coryanne_Wylde\" title=\"Coryanne Wylde\">Coryanne Wylde</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rosamund_Ball\" title=\"Rosamund Ball\">Rosamund Ball</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wise_Women&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, A Surfeit of Rulers.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404194353\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.010 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.011 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 119/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8538/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 339/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 104/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 580/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    6.010      1 -total\n 76.01%    4.568      1 Template:Ref\n 48.87%    2.937      1 Template:Ref/core\n 22.70%    1.364      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westero